Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\fad(1500,0)}服務區外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無需擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會殺你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們可是我重要的殺手鑭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣在面對4th時就能佔優
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能扭轉Dead End
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不滿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要阿雪能活下去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一開始是個莫名其妙的跟蹤狂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就算那樣 也算是滿腦子都在為我考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長得又可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去交涉的時候 雪輝你就在醫院裡進行偵察
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻負責監視人質和保持跟雪輝的聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:02:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去偵察？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左邊和右邊 你選哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這個你拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔掉安全環 打開保險的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5秒就會爆炸 很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪 把這個也帶上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒子彈了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我還是由乃拿著更好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這次能化險為夷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…想讓你陪我一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有地方想帶由乃一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨流美彌音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你毫不驚訝就說明是在等我對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說正事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人質的交換條件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的要求是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須圭吾自殺並為我們準備逃跑用的車子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突擊準備已經一切就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:23.32,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經是甕中之鱉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對無法從這裡逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧 你們別無選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是有人質在手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會了 9th
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要提出條件的是這邊才對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還正常嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不答應我的要求 你的兒子就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在這裡讓步 也無法拯救我的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有除了成為「神」以外的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能前進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全隊強行突入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上離開那裡 阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人攻進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已制服目標
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪 阿雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉失敗了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…居然連這種東西都有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須警官馬上就過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須先生…來須先生他來了的話我會被殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人質在413號病房
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要到達那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您認真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有上頭的許可就強攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西島
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我回警署去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課…課長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃…不逃的話會被殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得逃走才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻 不會讓你為所欲為的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝就當我的人質吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的人質 雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在那裡別動！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我就殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:51.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我就引爆它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了 我妻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話我就炸飛一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五分鐘後爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話多少能吸引些注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不認為這樣能扭轉Dead End
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在只能逃到哪算哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做個交易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻 我會釋放雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換 你也把你手上那個危險的東西丟掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝 你退下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由…由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的哦 阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿雪你給了原本如同行屍走肉一樣的我未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來當你未來的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我們長大後再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能快點長大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長大了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點長大…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪是我活下去的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果連這一點都不能實現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我要為阿雪而死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:08:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就算死去 我也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠追隨阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就和我一起死在這裡吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 由乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要和由乃一起去看星星…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨…雨流美彌音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於抓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:39.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝那小子 用了那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:58.81,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(622,660)}Flashbang
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃光雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:10:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃光彈啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是障眼法而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真貨對他來說負擔太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.82,0:10:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這算什麼障眼法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 剛剛的爆炸在4樓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我設置的炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩傢伙沒死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇見你之後 我知道逃出這個Dead End的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真走運啊 雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其他刑警到達之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會殺了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來一切就都解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧 雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不會開槍的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 你又會開槍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是朝著我妻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把槍扔了 否則我就割開我妻的脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我手一抖可就什麼都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4th
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 你會怎麼做？雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算開槍 如果射偏了的話 由乃就沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 射出的子彈也可能會擊中由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來日記上…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}20:10 [櫻見醫院內二樓 ICU]\N子彈會擊中由乃\N由乃死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會擊中由乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不能開槍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}6/13 20:10\N阿雪開槍了哦\N因為阿雪射出的子彈\N我死掉了\N天野雪輝射殺了2nd
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍的話 就會擊中由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日記上難道寫著什麼不好的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉色鐵青啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算棄槍我們也會被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍吧 阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算被射殺了也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是為阿雪而死的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算阿雪你是撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也說了我們是戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是裝裝樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也陪我參加了婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經足夠幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 我妻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼「幸福」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒空奉陪你們的戀人遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會隨身攜帶這種照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃難道不想變得更幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是個超級跟蹤狂 追趕了我一整年對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要當我的新娘不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果無法實現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有阿雪也好…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說什麼「無法實現」啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓由乃你得到幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:13:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算由乃放棄了 我也不會放棄的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂來 雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在乎由乃死活了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會放棄的 因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡由乃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以死…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可以死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來…來須先生 住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成為神的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為神 我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了 課長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像趕上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西島
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月島狩人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有想要陷害雪輝他們的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨流美彌音已經坦白了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道相信恐怖分子嗎 西島
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你做個交易
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交易？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我暫時不會攻擊你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:35.67,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會繼續透露警察的情報給你 提供方便
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把凶器扔掉 課長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經不是刑警了 只是個罪犯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去搜查權限的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無法透過搜查日記進行預知了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的未來日記被封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}6/13 20:10\N沒有警察情報\N6/13 20:22\N被雨流美彌音的槍射殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的老婆和兒子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經在爆炸前被SAT救出了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9th 雖然很自說自話 但是能不能再次和我結成同盟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代價是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的兒子就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也明白這不是道歉就能算了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35\fad(0,200)}6/13 20:10 [櫻見醫院內2樓 ICU]\N子彈會擊中由乃\N由乃死掉了\N6/13 20:11 [櫻見醫院內2樓 ICU]\N我被4th射殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35\fad(130,0)}6/13 20:10 [櫻見醫院內2樓 ICU]\N6/13 20:11 [櫻見醫院內2樓 ICU]\NDead End迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後 事件的處理交給了西島先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然我和由乃也受到了嚴厲的追查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但透過來須先生留在檔案裡的「真相」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多數誤會都解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須先生是否早就預料到會有這一刻？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今已經無從得知了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然來須先生的事件在世間引起了很大的反響
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們的事沒有被報道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後9th好像逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 已經這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說有什麼好事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我開槍射中的刑警保住了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來該怎麼辦啊 阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我想先去爸爸那裡一趟 借個望遠鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後爬上高一點的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說有人生中最棒的Happy End的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都想選今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃還真是小題大做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都想讓這一瞬間延續到永遠了 阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻也稍微熟練一點了呢 阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別調戲我啦 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此電話由於客戶要求而無法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此電話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡不上爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電車到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑過去吧 阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正還有時間 我稍微去下洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便買點什麼飲料回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}盡量不要和我妻同學走的太近\N為了調查取證 警察正在搜尋我妻同學\N但她卻失蹤了\N請務必要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋瀨或
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}郵件已刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪 這個還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有收到郵件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是騷擾郵件哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…就不能少帶點東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 因為裡面放著很重要的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西這麼重要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內衣啊毛巾啊藥啊 還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:17.00,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------ED--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:41.09,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心が死ぬよ 自分のためらいが引き金になるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:41.09,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}放任心死 自身的躊躇成為一切的誘因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:43.60,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「助けて」君へと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:43.60,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}向你呼喊著求救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:49.27,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「信じて」君から漏れた声に揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:49.27,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「相信我」因你吐出的話語而動搖不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:52.42,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}奇跡を祈ろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:52.42,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想要祈求奇跡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:57.49,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけど悲劇は終わらない鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:57.49,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}可悲劇是永遠不會停歇的鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:21:01.52,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闇の奥で繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:21:01.52,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在黑暗深處不斷重複
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:05.95,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}叫び 痛み 怒り 悪意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:05.95,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嘶吼 痛楚 憤怒 惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:09.28,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}選ばれし Blood teller
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:09.28,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}被選擇的Blood teller
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:13.62,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}泣きたくない これ以上会いたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:13.62,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不想哭泣 亦不願再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:17.46,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}燃える愛しさが交差した
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:17.46,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}燃燒的愛意互相交錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:21.70,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}会いにきて 泣きたくて追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:21.70,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}來見我吧 泫然欲泣一路追趕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:25.83,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰にもとめられない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:25.83,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}沒有任何人可以阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:30.34,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}これは未来? それとも夢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:30.34,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這是未來？還是夢幻？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.34,0:21:33.85,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}答えはどこだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.34,0:21:33.85,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}答案究竟位於何處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:38.45,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}これが今を試す扉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:38.45,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這是試煉今朝的門扉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:44.95,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}壊すの? 開けるの? どうしよう?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:44.95,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}破壞？還是打開？到底該如何選擇？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs42}穆魯穆魯老師的裡未來日記
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(753,461)}4th的原委
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.47,0:21:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(825,566)}咖啡店「隱之家」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:22:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 你也被選為12名日記持有者的其中之一了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維也納咖啡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣 請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候 我很想要塑料模型
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.55,0:22:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢達
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 聽著就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班裡的人都讓我選扎古
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我果然還是喜歡敢達
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比起敢達…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.79,0:22:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我成為刑警的原委
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.90,0:22:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管三七二十一從商店裡偷了一個出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.53,0:22:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管三七二十一…也就是說？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事被老爹發現後 我被揍的很慘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就想當刑警?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好那時候老爹也偷了別人家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話題看來會很長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.86,0:22:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到安定工作的老爹人間蒸發
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.74,0:22:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後弄壞了身體死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.70,0:23:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今我仍然在想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼當時沒有人去痛扁老爹一頓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.96,0:23:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.20,0:23:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是為了揍人才成為刑警的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜查日記
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西我就心存感激的收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了獨自一人也能痛扁他人一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小臘腸還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.33,0:23:48.04,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(3800,0)\fs80\pos(640,500)}主叫隱藏